1. Go to the official Node.js website: https://nodejs.org
2. Download the Windows Installer (.msi file).
3. Installed Node.js.
4. Check the installed version of nodejs using `node -v` (version 20.10.0)
5. Check the installed version of npm using `npm -v` (version 10.2.3)
6. Installed SASS using `npm install -g sass`.
7. Check the installed version of sass using `sass -version` (version 1.82.0)
